-- Zorlu to Bid for Turkish Coal Mine Development, Power Plant
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-08-28T06:00:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/zorlu-to-bid-for-turkish-coal-mine-development-power-plant.html
Zorlu Enerji Elektrik Uretim AS (ZOREN) , a
Turkish electricity producer, is bidding in a government auction
to develop a coal mine and build a coal-fired power plant with
at least 450 megawatts capacity, the company said in a stock-
exchange filing. The auction deadline is today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
